{"tid":2142604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬克龍抵貝魯特 尋求與政治各方達成改革共識","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T05:06:46.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2386ad3c57a4f422dd26e4624eba06553f070243","tid":2142604,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"馬克龍抵貝魯特 尋求與政治各方達成改革共識<br />\n2020-08-06 HKT 19:59<br />\n<br />\n&quot;黎巴嫩首都貝魯特大爆炸，死亡人數上升至145人，最少5000人受傷，多人仍然失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n曾經管治黎巴嫩的法國，總統馬克龍乘坐攜同救援物資的專機抵達當地視察，指黎巴嫩正面臨政治與經濟危機，除非推行改革，否則將繼續遭受苦難，他會尋求與黎巴嫩政治各方達成共識.....&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542242-20200806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542242-20200806.htm&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=3cf9be6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542242-20200806.htm&h=ba62dcc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542242-20200806.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8b30c8f8e2fe9f7b9fd159f42e327d77af1024bb","tid":2142604,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"馬克龍到訪期間，大批貝魯特市民向他表達對黎巴嫩政府的不滿，指責高層存在貪污，對妥善處理大批化學品長期疏忽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殖民主走後，社會就倒退<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efdaf9f7b12e8f8161383d57c93de9e301dcfbb","tid":2142604,"uid":162535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"tankies又然<br />\n黎巴嫩人肯定係帝國主義 白人至上 殖民主義啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f4141106d89266aa89574157be939e4beb9851","tid":2142604,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"中東巴黎變到咁，好慘"},{"pid":"3c396f8272210bd1a122c00df78efc4a26afdbd5","tid":2142604,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply